00:00:00.274 --> 00:00:02.127
 Welcome to Jawbone Customer Support 

00:00:02.456 --> 00:00:05.269
 In this video, let's take a look at the different modes of the bracelet. 

00:00:05.391 --> 00:00:06.961
 let us start 

00:00:07.156 --> 00:00:08.878
 The bracelet has four different modes 

00:00:09.113 --> 00:00:13.822
 Awake mode, sleep mode, stopwatch mode, nap mode 

00:00:14.270 --> 00:00:16.015
 Switching between different modes is easy 

00:00:16.316 --> 00:00:18.763
 Awake mode is used to monitor the pace of the day 

00:00:19.124 --> 00:00:21.104
 This is the default mode of the bracelet 

00:00:22.461 --> 00:00:25.109
 Sleep mode is used as tracking 

00:00:25.148 --> 00:00:26.829
 The quality and quantity of your shallow sleep 

00:00:27.125 --> 00:00:29.750
 To turn on sleep mode, press the bracelet button 

00:00:29.758 --> 00:00:32.497
 Until the bracelet vibrates and the moon sign flashes 

00:00:32.892 --> 00:00:34.456
 Flashing color or change 

00:00:34.476 --> 00:00:36.370
 Depending on the type of bracelet 

00:00:36.870 --> 00:00:39.564
 To switch back to awake mode, press and hold the bracelet button 

00:00:40.026 --> 00:00:42.818
 The bracelet will vibrate and the sun sign will flash 

00:00:43.220 --> 00:00:45.415
 Please note that you must switch back to awake mode 

00:00:45.426 --> 00:00:47.215
 Can switch to other modes 

00:00:47.723 --> 00:00:49.626
 Stopwatch mode for monitoring 

00:00:49.656 --> 00:00:51.379
 You are in a certain time 

00:00:51.409 --> 00:00:53.284
 Or the pace of a particular event 

00:00:53.441 --> 00:00:56.197
 Such as a basketball game or a dance class 

00:00:56.771 --> 00:00:59.595
 To start the stopwatch mode, double-click the bracelet button twice. 

00:00:59.639 --> 00:01:01.452
 Hold down the second 

00:01:01.723 --> 00:01:04.293
 When you start the stopwatch mode, your bracelet will vibrate 

00:01:04.317 --> 00:01:06.527
 The sun sign will flash three times 

00:01:07.468 --> 00:01:10.163
 Nap mode helps you calculate the best time for a sleep cycle 

00:01:10.192 --> 00:01:12.337
 And wake you up in a slight vibration 

00:01:12.716 --> 00:01:15.679
 To start the nap mode, double-click the button on the bracelet. 

00:01:15.692 --> 00:01:17.521
 Finally hold it down 

00:01:17.660 --> 00:01:20.382
 When you activate the nap mode, your bracelet will vibrate 

00:01:20.402 --> 00:01:22.661
 The moon sign will flash three times 

00:01:23.346 --> 00:01:25.225
 If you are not sure what mode the bracelet is in 

00:01:25.260 --> 00:01:27.265
 Press the bracelet button once to view 

00:01:27.654 --> 00:01:30.511
 The bracelet logo will flash to indicate the mode it is in. 

00:01:30.784 --> 00:01:33.671
 If you have a UP 24, you can also 

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:35.852
 Open the app on your phone or iPad to check the bracelet mode 

00:01:36.226 --> 00:01:38.074
 Bracelet mode logo will 

00:01:38.086 --> 00:01:40.209
 Displayed in the upper right corner of the home screen 

00:01:40.587 --> 00:01:43.049
 If your bracelet is in awake mode 

00:01:43.055 --> 00:01:44.736
 A bracelet icon with no status will appear 

00:01:45.128 --> 00:01:48.267
 You can also switch between different bracelet modes using the UP app. 

00:01:48.680 --> 00:01:51.478
 Click the bracelet icon in the top right corner of the home screen 

00:01:51.487 --> 00:01:52.974
 To open the correct menu 

00:01:53.076 --> 00:01:55.887
 Just click on the mode you want to turn it on or off. 

00:01:56.129 --> 00:01:58.511
 Thank you for watching, enjoy UP! 

